# Test fixtures are byte-exact snapshot data. Never apply EOL conversion:
# on Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true on GitHub's windows runners) LF
# would be rewritten to CRLF, corrupting the bytes so golden comparisons
# fail against the renderer's LF output. See candy-shine / sugar-table
# GoldenRenderTest + RendererTest.
**/tests/fixtures/** -text

# Belt-and-suspenders for snapshot files wherever they live.
*.golden -text
*.ansi   -text
*.tape   -text
